statements.sql: select `bills`.*, (select sum(`payments`.`pay`) from `payments` where `bills`.`id` = `payments`.`bill_id` and `payments`.`deleted_at` is null) as `payments_sum_pay`, (select sum(`spendings`.`nominal`) from `spendings` where `bills`.`id` = `spendings`.`bill_id` and `spendings`.`deleted_at` is null) as `spendings_sum_nominal` from `bills` where `bills`.`deleted_at` is null order by `payments_sum_pay` desc
select sum(`pay`) as aggregate from `payments` where `pay_date` = '2024-06-29' and `payments`.`deleted_at` is null
select sum(`pay`) as aggregate from `payments` where `pay_date` = '2024-06-30' and `payments`.`deleted_at` is null
select sum(`pay`) as aggregate from `payments` where `pay_date` between '2024-06-16' and '2024-06-23' and `payments`.`deleted_at` is null
select sum(`pay`) as aggregate from `payments` where `pay_date` between '2024-06-23' and '2024-06-30' and `payments`.`deleted_at` is null
select sum(`pay`) as aggregate from `payments` where `pay_date` between '2024-05-01' and '2024-05-30' and `payments`.`deleted_at` is null
select sum(`pay`) as aggregate from `payments` where `pay_date` between '2024-06-01' and '2024-06-30' and `payments`.`deleted_at` is null
select sum(`pay`) as aggregate from `payments` where year(`pay_date`) = '2023' and `payments`.`deleted_at` is null
select sum(`pay`) as aggregate from `payments` where year(`pay_date`) = '2024' and `payments`.`deleted_at` is null

select SUM(`payments`.`pay`) as total, `bills`.`name`, `payments`.`pay_date` from `bills` left join `payments` on `bills`.`id` = `payments`.`bill_id` where `bills`.`deleted_at` is null and `payments`.`deleted_at` is null and `payments`.`pay_date` between '2024-06-23' and '2024-06-30' group by `bills`.`id` order by `total` asc

select SUM(`spendings`.`nominal`) as total, `bills`.`name`, `spendings`.`spending_date` from `bills` left join `spendings` on `bills`.`id` = `spendings`.`bill_id` where `bills`.`deleted_at` is null and `spendings`.`deleted_at` is null and `spendings`.`spending_date` between '2024-06-23' and '2024-06-30' group by `bills`.`id` order by `total` asc

select `permissions`.*, `model_has_permissions`.`model_uuid` as `pivot_model_uuid`, `model_has_permissions`.`permission_id` as `pivot_permission_id`, `model_has_permissions`.`model_type` as `pivot_model_type` from `permissions` inner join `model_has_permissions` on `permissions`.`id` = `model_has_permissions`.`permission_id` where `model_has_permissions`.`model_uuid` = '71df8281-cfc5-4f9d-96ca-1399e465c738' and `model_has_permissions`.`model_type` = 'Modules\Master\Entities\User'
select column_name as `column_name` from information_schema.columns where table_schema = 'aplikasi-spp' and table_name = 'roles'
